message.body: How are things going over there? Will probably be ready to get there around 10. How's that sound? Do you need us to bring anything for you?
Cooper is still sleeping but we are getting ready.
That is crazy! Let me know what works for you guys. It takes us about 20 min longer to get there tan you
We'll just meet inside in case we are a few min late. We will wait until last second to wake him.
He is waking up now. So we should be good
Sounds good, see you soon! Avery is beyond excited, watch out ;)
We haven't left yet so it'll be a little after 10
Just leaving now. So go ahead and get in and we will meet you wherever you are
Ok call when you get there. We are just by Tacoma mall
